snippet.title: Ara and the Empty Universe | Release date Trailer
snippet.description:
Ara and the Empty Universe will be coming May 31st on itch.io and maybe some other stores.

Here's my itchio page where the game will be sold: https://basim-el-hout.itch.io/


Song used in video: The Hive - by Kevin Macleod.
